        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your physique is so impressive that your acts of strength astound your foes. When you succeed or critically succeed at an Athletics check to [[/act grapple]], [[/act reposition]], [[/act shove]], or [[/act trip]], you can, as a free action, attempt an Athletics or Intimidation check to [[/act demoralize]] one creature within 30 feet. You also gain the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Intimidating Glare] skill feat, even if you don't meet the prerequisites.</p>"
